Package: popdictR
Type: Package
Title: A package designed to measure populism in text with a German dictionary.
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Johann Gründl
Maintainer: Johann Gründl <mail@johanngruendl.at>
Description: With this package I bundled my populism dictionary for German
    social media content. It includes the dictionary, all terms considered
    during the development, and functions to easily apply the dictionary to
    textual data.
Depends: R (>= 2.10)
License: CC0
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
